The evidence with the title 'Eric Schmidt - Wikipedia ' says Eric Emerson Schmidt (born april 27, 1955) is an American businessman and software engineer . He is known for being the executive chairman of Google from 2001 to 2015 and Alphabet Inc. from 2015 to 2017 . In 2017, Forbes ranked Schmidt as the 119th - richest person in the world, ... From 1997 to 2001 , he was chief executive officer ( ceo ) of Novell.
